<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1885-07-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1885-07-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="17" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d17">
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">No. 17.</seg></opener>
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Francis</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Bayard</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Vienna</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-07-27"><hi rend="italic">July</hi> 27,
                            1885</date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p rend="flushleft"><hi rend="smallcaps">Bayard</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi></p>
                    <p>Conference Saturday. He will answer soon. Take leave Friday. Lee arrived.</p>
                    <closer><signed>FRANCIS</signed></closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>